
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Contact Us";
}


<div class="row" style="background-color :#f7f9fa;">
    <div class="col" style="display:flex ;  justify-content: center;align-items: center;">
        <h2 class="text-center" style="font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">Connecting people with knowledge</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col" style="display:block">
        <img src="~/assets/images/section-bg.jpg" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius:8px " alt="photo" />
    </div>

    
</div>

<div class="row text-center" style="margin-top:100px;font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">
    <h3 style="font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">
        Our origins
    </h3>
    <p style="padding-left: 400px; padding-right: 400px;font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">
        Growing up in a small Turkish village, Udemy founder Eren Bali had few educational opportunities — until he got a computer. Fueled by his dream to compete in mathematics, he used the internet to learn his way to a silver medal in the International Math Olympiad.


        After learning online changed his life, Eren partnered with co-founders Oktay Caglar and Gagan Biyani to achieve a common goal: to make quality education accessible to all.
    </p>
</div>
